  "subject": "State that Casablanca is not security maintained",
  "commit_message": "State that Casablanca is not security maintained\n\nAccording to recently updated Vulnerability Management Procedure we\nare going to develop security fixes for master and the latest release.\nFollowing TSC recommendation Casablanca release is excluded from that\nrule.\n\nIn order to make community fully aware of that, let's add this info to\nCassablanca release notes.\n\nIssue-ID: SECCOM-216\nChange-Id: I3c1d963c1c97535160455b1e363b5bf979fc2a25\nSigned-off-by: Krzysztof Opasiak <k.opasiak@samsung.com>\n",
